'''Artusian [[Mining/Legends|mining]] drills''' were used in the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] mines of [[Artus Prime]]. Heavy and clunky, they were operated by [[Slavery/Legends|slave]] laborers. [[Kyle Katarn]] used a mining drill to gain access to a restricted section of the mining operation in the events leading up to the [[Battle of Artus Prime]].

